BusinessTech’s dedicated mailers are the best way for you to get your marketing message to a large South African audience. These mailers allow you to distribute your marketing message to the inboxes of BusinessTech’s 185,000 newsletter subscribers. The majority of these subscribers are important decision-makers in their homes and businesses, including many C-level executives, business owners, company directors, and other professionals. This makes BusinessTech’s mailers an excellent way to reach influential South Africans directly with your brand and story. BusinessTech’s direct mailer marketing solutions are managed by our talented marketing team. These professionals will design your HTML mailer (if required), distribute it, and provide you with performance reports on your campaign. Click here to find out more about advertising on BusinessTech.